{"tid":565555,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"95歲資深演員侯煥玲離世 曾參演《喜劇之王》《六樓后座》等電影","createTime":"2018-02-19T05:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T11:22:46.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1399f2efe2a217f058628d06f105bd074a535d9b","tid":565555,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gtiNIDOfTFqUg9azbipnwA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180219f081011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgtiNIDOfTFqUg9azbipnwA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180219f081011.jpg&h=475b279c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】曾參與電影《審死官》、《喜劇之王》、《回魂夜》以及《六樓后座》等電影的資深演員侯煥玲婆婆，於睡夢中離世，享年95歲。侯煥玲婆婆的死訊，今日凌晨12時許由邵音音於社交網站發佈，她稱：「她夢中走過。感恩黃大仙醫院及義工們的照顧。她安詳又平靜！」<br />\n<br />\n邵音音稱：「別難過。她走得很好。褔！好人一生平安。她走得好。大家祝福她。感恩大家對她的愛。她是多幸福！她從三藩市回來，她好喜歡香港，好喜歡電影，好喜歡周星馳，她是個快樂人。」<br />\n<br />\n侯煥玲婆婆67歲才踏入影圈，有「星爺御用阿婆」的稱號，她為人熟悉的電影，包括與周星馳首次合作的《審死官》，她在《破壞王》飾演為孫兒買張學友個唱門票的阿婆、《喜劇之王》中飾演洪爺的阿婆，亦令人難忘。侯婆婆最後一部電影，是2013年的《迷離夜》，之後曾客串拍VR廣告大玩Cosplay，依然精靈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/95%E6%AD%B2%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E4%BE%AF%E7%85%A5%E7%8E%B2%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%83%E6%BC%94-%E5%96%9C%E5%8A%87%E4%B9%8B%E7%8E%8B-%E5%85%AD%E6%A8%93%E5%90%8E%E5%BA%A7-%E7%AD%89%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-000200747.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F95%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BE%25AF%25E7%2585%25A5%25E7%258E%25B2%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%258F%2583%25E6%25BC%2594-%25E5%2596%259C%25E5%258A%2587%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%258E%258B-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2590%258E%25E5%25BA%25A7-%25E7%25AD%2589%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1-000200747.html&d=NOwHBB%2FopAcSV4JlwH5FeuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=c78f969a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/95%E6%AD%B2%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E4%BE%AF%E7%85%A5%E7%8E%B2%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%83%E6%BC%94-%E5%96%9C%E5%8A%87%E4%B9%8B%E7%8E%8B-%E5%85%AD%E6%A8%93%E5%90%8E%E5%BA%A7-%E7%AD%89%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-000200747.html</a>"},{"pid":"ac6f285c554c4c91af6c66ba597abb86960ddd6e","tid":565555,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"無錯 我係死人頭"},{"pid":"39a909c89f3f26d93a698755c5c17004dc85095c","tid":565555,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"侯婆婆一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593b3ddf0246fe20d8510fbb38d88dd3ffa299eb","tid":565555,"uid":28619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"Rip 奶奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}